      <title>俄罗斯将减少战争中受伤士兵的工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/russia-to-reduce-payments-for-soldiers-wounded-in-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着入侵成本的不断增加，俄罗斯政府正在减少向乌克兰战争中受伤较轻的士兵支付的赔偿金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/russia-to-reduce-payments-for-soldiers-wounded-in-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 06:42:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在骚乱后部分重新开放莫桑比克边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/south-africa-partially-reopens-mozambique-border-after-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于前一天发生抗议活动，南非与莫桑比克的主要边境暂停通行，周四上午，南非开始允许部分边境通行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/south-africa-partially-reopens-mozambique-border-after-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 06:14:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国同性婚姻法有望带来 20 亿美元“彩虹旅游”收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/thailand-set-for-2-billion-rainbow-tourism-boon-with-same-sex-marriage-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据旅游平台 Agoda 称，泰国同性婚姻合法化的里程碑之举将推动“彩虹旅游”的发展，每年将吸引 400 万游客，并产生约 20 亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/thailand-set-for-2-billion-rainbow-tourism-boon-with-same-sex-marriage-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 05:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>价格僵局致英国癌症患者无法获得药物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/nhs-drug-pricing-standoff-denies-cancer-patients-treatment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[药品定价监管机构、制药公司和政府因获得延长寿命的疗法而争吵不休。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/nhs-drug-pricing-standoff-denies-cancer-patients-treatment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 05:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选让首尔重新考虑向乌克兰提供武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/trump-s-win-gives-seoul-second-thoughts-about-arms-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利促使韩国重新考虑直接向乌克兰运送武器的可能性，这一决定可能对战争走向产生重大影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/trump-s-win-gives-seoul-second-thoughts-about-arms-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉拥抱习近平引发特朗普对华政策冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/brazil-s-embrace-of-china-for-economic-growth-tests-trump-tariff-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统希望北京帮助该国经济发展。这一策略可能会与特朗普发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/brazil-s-embrace-of-china-for-economic-growth-tests-trump-tariff-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
